    <h3>Lowland Expertise</h3>
    <p>
        Lowland Expertise is a buff you can purchase from each heart in Janthir Wilds. At 7 stacks, it gives 5% Damage vs titanspawn.
        You can farm all 7 stacks in a single day, as there are 3 hearts in Lowland Shores, 3 hearts in Janthir Syntri, and 1 heart in Mistburned Barrens.
    </p>
    <p>
        Each time you buy LE from a finished heart, it adds a stack, capping at 7. It also adds 4 hours to the timer, capping at 24 hours.
        You should only need to do the hearts every couple days to keep the buff up, as it doesn't tick unless you're logged in on that character. 
        If you let it expire, you will need to redo all 7 stacks.
    </p>
